Google built safety considerations into Gemini's architecture from the start, rather than adding them as an afterthought. The system includes multiple layers of alignment training, constitutional AI principles, and filtering mechanisms designed to reduce hallucinations – those problematic instances where AI generates confident-sounding but false information.

